          "date": "2013-04-29 16:34:43.000000000",
          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-2797 osc: GPF in osc_send_oap_rpc",
        "message": "LU-2797 osc: GPF in osc_send_oap_rpc\n\nDue to cl_loi_list_lock release in osc_send_oap_rpc(), this\nleaves a window where lov_oinfo may be freed/poisoned when\nback from both write/read steps/calls of osc_send_oap_rpc()\nin osc_check_rpcs(). To avoid this, loi is unlinked from\nall client_obd cl_loi_[hp_ready,ready,write_read]_list's\nand all intermediate loi_list_maint() calls to relink it\nhave been removed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ic9b754cf690142e8599a9d8201ea8b907459f3a4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
